<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-a-ones-hurry">in a / one's hurry</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>匆忙；急于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was in a hurry to leave.
他急着要离开。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In his hurry to catch the train, he left his book in the taxi.
他匆匆忙忙地去赶火车，把书落在了出租车里。</p></div></div>